The Bank of England said it provided themarket with a further 442 mln stg assistance during the morningto offset a liquidity shortage it estimated at 1.60 billionstg, revised up from 1.55 billion    The bank bought outright eight mln stg of band one treasurybills and five mln stg of band one bank bills at 10-3/8 pct.    It bought a further 429 mln stg of bills for resale to thediscount houses on April 2 at an interest rate of 10-7/16 pct.    So far today, the bank has given the market assistanceworth a total of 1.501 billion stg. REUTER&#3;